I spend a TON of time here...as I do at my fan boards.  Yes, I AM addicted to the boards (I admit it).  I can NOT play EQ from work...but I CAN jump on here for a few minutes when I have down time at work between patients and try to LEARN some stuff, be SOCIAL with the EQ community, etc.  I don't really see why people care, honestly, it is my life and posting habit, not theirs.  If I want to read/post for 15 minutes here and there throughout the day INSTEAD of picking up a newspaper, a book, a magazine, etc.  Who really GAFF?!  Some seem to be very interested in my habits, odd!  Personally, I think they should worry more about themselves than me.<br>
